explain it to me.

30:54.568 --> 30:56.904
I don't owe you an explanation.

30:57.113 --> 31:00.741
I owe you an apology,
and I have apologised.

31:00.950 --> 31:03.744
I am very sorry, Gretchen.

31:03.953 --> 31:06.914
There. I've apologised twice now.

31:07.123 --> 31:10.001
I'm humbly sorry.

31:10.209 --> 31:11.669
Three times.

31:11.877 --> 31:13.838
Let me just get this straight.

31:14.046 --> 31:16.424
Elliott and I offer
to pay for your treatment...

31:16.632 --> 31:18.092
...no strings attached.

31:18.300 --> 31:20.511
An offer which still stands,
by the way.

31:20.720 --> 31:23.389
And you turn us down out of pride,
whatever...

31:23.597 --> 31:28.019
...and then you tell your wife that in
fact we are paying for your treatment.

31:28.227 --> 31:30.062
Without our knowledge,
against our will...

31:30.271 --> 31:32.273
...you involve us in your lie.

31:32.481 --> 31:38.362
And you sit here and tell me
that that is none of my business?

31:40.364 --> 31:44.327
Yeah.
That's pretty much the size of it.

31:46.829 --> 31:49.206
What happened to you?

31:52.084 --> 31:54.211
Really, Walt.

31:54.420 --> 31:56.213
What happened?

31:56.422 --> 31:59.216
Because this isn't you.

32:02.261 --> 32:06.140
What would you know about me,
Gretchen?

32:06.349 --> 32:10.770
What would your presumption
about me be, exactly?

32:10.978 --> 32:13.314
That I should go begging
for your charity?

32:14.023 --> 32:17.360
And you waving
your chequebook around...

32:17.568 --> 32:21.113
...like some magic wand
is gonna make me forget...

32:21.322 --> 32:22.448
...how you and Elliott-

32:22.657 --> 32:25.743
How you and Elliott cut me out?

32:25.951 --> 32:27.745
What? That can't be how you see it.

32:27.953 --> 32:31.415
It was my hard work, my research,
and you and Elliott make millions off it.

32:31.624 --> 32:33.542
That cannot be how you see it.

32:33.751 --> 32:35.670
Good. That's beautifully done.
-You left-

32:35.878 --> 32:37.672
You are always
the picture of innocence.

32:37.880 --> 32:40.424
You left me.
-The picture of innocence.

32:40.633 --> 32:44.178
Just sweetness and light.
-You left me.

32:44.970 --> 32:46.263
Newport, 4th of July weekend.

32:46.472 --> 32:49.600
You and my father and my brothers
and I go up to our room...

32:49.809 --> 32:52.395
...and you're packing your bags,
barely talking.

32:52.603 --> 32:55.272
What? Did I dream all of that?

32:55.481 --> 32:57.983
That's your excuse...

32:58.192 --> 33:00.986
...to build your little empire
on my work?

33:01.195 --> 33:03.447
How can you say that to me?
You walked away.

33:03.656 --> 33:06.701
You abandoned us, me, Elliott.

33:06.909 --> 33:09.620
Little rich girl
just adding to your millions.

33:14.041 --> 33:17.628
I don't even know what to say to you.

33:18.337 --> 33:21.382
I don't even know where to begin.

33:26.679 --> 33:32.018
I feel so sorry for you, Walt.

33:34.603 --> 33:37.148
Fuck you.

34:12.766 --> 34:14.685
Hey.

34:17.730 --> 34:21.275
Hey, little man, you hungry?

34:35.081 --> 34:36.623
