36:20.853 --> 36:22.563
Never mind.

36:22.772 --> 36:25.775
We're long past that, I suppose.

36:26.859 --> 36:28.694
Skyler.

36:34.825 --> 36:38.245
Gretchen called about an hour ago.

36:48.673 --> 36:50.341
Walt.

36:51.217 --> 36:53.511
We need to talk.

37:05.272 --> 37:07.149
Just say it.

37:16.951 --> 37:19.829
They're cutting off the money.

37:31.590 --> 37:34.552
