37:47.440 --> 37:51.360
"I'm sorry to have to do this...

37:51.569 --> 37:56.157
...but Elliott and I can no longer
continue to pay for Walt's treatment.

37:56.365 --> 37:59.452
I wish you the very best."

38:01.203 --> 38:03.497
And that was it.

38:09.170 --> 38:10.755
Yeah.

38:11.422 --> 38:15.676
I mean, she sounded apologetic.
I guess.

38:15.885 --> 38:17.803
It was quick.
She got right off the phone.

38:18.012 --> 38:20.514
I was so stunned, but...

38:20.723 --> 38:25.644
