39:13.943 --> 39:15.194
I was with Gretchen.

39:15.403 --> 39:18.656
Well, Gretchen and Elliott.

39:19.740 --> 39:24.412
She just couldn't bring
herself to tell you today.

39:24.620 --> 39:27.498
I mean, she couldn't tell me,
either, really.

39:27.707 --> 39:30.835
I mean, there was
a lot of hemming and hawing...

39:31.043 --> 39:32.920
...and beating around the bush-

39:33.129 --> 39:37.008
Okay, what-? Tell us what?

39:38.759 --> 39:40.511
Well...

39:42.471 --> 39:43.514
